OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe billionaire facing     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdeath over $44bn bank fraud
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, It is the most spectacular trial ever  
OL,6, held in Vietnam, befitting one of the  
OL,7, greatest bank frauds the world has ever
OL,8, seen.                                  
OL,10,FBehind the stately yellow portico of   
OL,11,Fthe colonial-era courthouse in Ho Chi  
OL,12,FMinh City, a 67-year-old property      
OL,13,Fdeveloper stands accused of looting one
OL,14,Fof Vietnam's largest banks over a      
OL,15,Fperiod of 11 years.                    
OL,17,FThe numbers involved are dizzying.     
OL,18,FTruong My Lan is charged with taking   
OL,19,Fout $44bn (#35bn) in loans from the    
OL,20,FSaigon Commercial Bank. Prosecutors say
OL,21,F$27bn may never be recovered.          
